## Sensitive Field Rules

These fields are NEVER included in list endpoints and NEVER returned without per-record auth:

| Field | Table | Rule |
|-------|-------|------|
| `session_summary` | sessions | Only to assigned counselor, assistant, or owner. Never in session lists. |
| `presenting_problem` | students | Only in detail view with verified access. Never in student lists. |
| `general_notes` | students | Same as presenting_problem. |
| `escalation_reason` | ai_analyses | Only to assigned counselor, assistant, or owner. |
| `counselor_notes` | ai_analyses | Same as escalation_reason. |

